longBusinessSummary: STS Group AG develops, manufactures, and supplies products and solutions for acoustic and thermal insulation, and components of plastics or composite materials for the automotive and truck industries in Europe and internationally. The company operates in three segments: Plastics, China, and Materials. The Plastics segment offers hard trim components, such as exterior body parts and interior modules for commercial vehicles and passenger cars. The China segment provides plastic components for commercial vehicles, such as bumpers, front paneling, deflectors, roofs, fenders and entrances, as well as battery covers for electric vehicles. The Materials segment produces and sells semi-finished goods, including sheet, bulk, and advanced molding compound products that are used for hard trim applications. The company was formerly known as mutares Holding-17 AG and changed its name to STS Group AG in February 2017. The company was founded in 1934 and is headquartered in Hallbergmoos, Germany.
